OL,5,G0340 Bradley & Barney Walsh: Breaking
OL,6,G     Dad
OL,7,     FThe actor and his son head for
OL,8,     FAustralia, and begin their latest
OL,9,     Fchallenge in Sydney. There they
OL,10,     Ftake in the sights of the famous
OL,11,     FSydney Harbour Bridge and Opera
OL,12,     FHouse with a terrifying aerobatic
OL,13,     Fflight. The next day the duo head
OL,14,     Fout of the city towards the
OL,15,     Fbeautiful Blue Mountains, but once
OL,16,     Fagain, Brad's fear of heights is
OL,17,     Fput to the test when they take a
OL,18,     Fride on what turns out to be an
OL,19,     Fextreme cable car
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
