OL,5,G0430 FIFA World Cup 2026
OL,6,     FAustralia v Turkiye (Kick-off
OL,7,     F5.00am). Laura Woods presents
OL,8,     Fcoverage of the Group D match at
OL,9,     FBC Place Vancouver in Canada. The
OL,10,     FSocceroos are appearing at their
OL,11,     Fsixth consecutive finals, and a
OL,12,     Fseventh overall, and will hope to
OL,13,     Fbuild on their experience in Qatar
OL,14,     Ffour years ago when they
OL,15,     Fprogressed to the knockout stage
OL,16,     Ffor just the second time. They
OL,17,     Ffaced European opposition twice in
OL,18,     Fthe group stage on that occasion
OL,19,     Fand had mixed fortunes, beginning
OL,20,     Ftheir campaign with a 4-1 loss to
OL,21,     Feventual runners-up France, before
OL,22,     Fbeating Denmark 1-0 in their final
